            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-600 to-cyan-600 text-white border-[3px] border-sky-400 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">DOMAIN & SEO PRESERVATION</h3>
      
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">DOMAIN TRANSFER</h4>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-white/40 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold mb-1">STEP 1: UNLOCK DOMAIN</p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                  At your current registrar, disable registrar lock. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-sky-200">Get EPP code (authorization key).</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-white/40 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold mb-1">STEP 2: REQUEST TRANSFER</p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                  Initiate transfer at new registrar/platform. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-sky-200">Approve confirmation emails.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-white/40 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold mb-1">STEP 3: WAIT 5-7 DAYS</p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                  Domain transfers take time. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-sky-200">Site stays live during transfer.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">SEO PROTECTION</h4>
