              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-white/40 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold mb-1">KEEP URL STRUCTURE</p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                  Match old page URLs exactly. <span class="font-bold text-sky-200">/about stays /about.</span>
                  Eliminates need for redirects.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-white/40 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold mb-1">SET UP 301 REDIRECTS</p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                  If URLs must change, redirect old ‚Üí new. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-sky-200">Preserves SEO ranking.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-white/40 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold mb-1">SUBMIT SITEMAP</p>
                <p class="text-sm">
                  New sitemap to Google Search Console. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-sky-200">Speeds re-indexing.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white/20 rounded-lg p-6">
        <p class="text-lg">
          <span class="font-bold">CRITICAL:</span> 
          <span class="underline">Don't cancel your old site until the new one is live and verified.</span>
          Build new site on a temporary URL, test everything, then swap domains. 
          This eliminates downtime and lets you fix issues before anyone sees them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-blue-500 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-blue-600">TIMELINE & DOWNTIME STRATEGY</h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-[2px] border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">RECOMMENDED 4-WEEK TIMELINE</h4>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-blue-400 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">WEEK 1: Audit & Export</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                  Inventory all content, export data, choose new platform. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">Don't cancel anything yet.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-blue-400 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">WEEK 2: Build New Site</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                  Rebuild core pages on temporary URL. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">Focus on structure, not perfection.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-sky-400 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">WEEK 3: Test & Refine</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                  Test all forms, links, functionality. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-sky-600">Fix broken images, check mobile, verify SEO.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-l-[4px] border-sky-400 pl-4">
                <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">WEEK 4: Launch & Monitor</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                  Swap domains, cancel old plan, monitor traffic/errors. 
                  <span class="font-bold text-sky-600">Keep old access for 30 days just in case.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-[2px] border-blue-300 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">ZERO-DOWNTIME SWITCH</h4>
          <ol class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><span class="font-bold text-blue-600">1.</span> Build new site on temp URL (newsite.yourplatform.com)</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold text-blue-600">2.</span> Test thoroughly - everything should work perfectly</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold text-blue-600">3.</span> Lower DNS TTL on old domain to 5 minutes (wait 24 hours)</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold text-blue-600">4.</span> Point domain DNS to new platform</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold text-blue-600">5.</span> Wait 5-30 minutes for propagation</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold text-blue-600">6.</span> Verify site loads from new platform</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold text-blue-600">7.</span> Cancel old plan once verified working</li>
          </ol>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-4">
            <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">RESULT:</span> Visitors see continuous site. No "under maintenance" page needed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

