          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <span class="font-bold text-sky-600">PREVENTION:</span> Never transfer domain until new site is verified live.
            Keep old registrar access for 30 days after switch. 
            <span class="underline">Domain registrars have recovery processes - use them if needed.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">DISASTER #2: SEO Traffic Drop</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <span class="font-bold text-sky-600">PREVENTION:</span> Keep identical URLs. If impossible, set up 301 redirects immediately.
            Submit new sitemap to Google. Monitor Search Console for crawl errors.
            <span class="underline">Traffic usually recovers in 2-4 weeks if redirects are correct.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">DISASTER #3: Broken Forms & Functionality</p>
