            Re-upload from originals, not from old site (which may compress).
            <span class="underline">Check image compression settings on new platform.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 mt-6">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800">
